space.arim.api.chat

Class MessageUtil

  • java.lang.Object
    • space.arim.api.chat.MessageUtil

  • public final class MessageUtil
extends Object
    Accepts formatted strings and converts them to a Message.

    Colour Parsing:
    * Uses '&' colour codes by default. (DEFAULT_FORMATTING_CHAR)
    * Does not add or convert Format.RESET codes, see Format.RESET for more information.
    * To use a colour code char other than the default '&', use FormattingCodePattern.
    Json Message Parsing:
    * Parses Minecraft Json messages, not JSON data objects.
    * Includes colour parsing by default.
    * Follows RezzedUp's JSON.sk format.
    Author:
    A248
